    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wacky perks - </strong>With overpowered synergies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse playstyles -</strong> Tons of cards, characters and build options.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Twitch API - </strong>Viewers can join as allied NPC's and create a custom loadout!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEVER ALONE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allies crash into battle with style, in drop pods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/cc2b677ebc071dd91c03065571fd4c8b.poster.avif?t=1746787200\" width=530 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/cc2b677ebc071dd91c03065571fd4c8b.webm?t=1746787200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/cc2b677ebc071dd91c03065571fd4c8b.mp4?t=1746787200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BE A CARDMANCER</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Real time deckbuilder.</strong> Spend energy to play cards - either summon allies, cast spells or just start blasting with conventional weaponry. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Channel your inner bard.</strong> Each character can play unique hymns to influence the battlefield whilst recharging their energy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WACKY SPELLS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each element has unique effects. You can even reverse gravity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/f5be2dffa7254295bf6652cc9bfe189f.poster.avif?t=1746787200\" width=360 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/f5be2dffa7254295bf6652cc9bfe189f.webm?t=1746787200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/f5be2dffa7254295bf6652cc9bfe189f.mp4?t=1746787200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY LOOP </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a planet on the dynamic campaign map. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Board your ship &amp; survive the journey into battle!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eject  &amp; reinforce your troops!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your deck, army and spacefleet - then launch into space to battle again. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FUN DETAILS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy an enemy ship in low orbit, it'll crash onto the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/f4669d13078817555d0bc37c83fc743c.poster.avif?t=1746787200\" width=490 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/f4669d13078817555d0bc37c83fc743c.webm?t=1746787200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223850/extras/f4669d13078817555d0bc37c83fc743c.mp4?t=1746787200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENLIST TODAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eradicate the demon scourge from our universe and restore prosperity to human race.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTRAS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Randomised enemy compositions.</strong> Enemies who can deflect bullets, shapeshifters, enemy artillery, bosses &amp; more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Curses!</strong> The enemy will periodically curse the battlefield with tactical effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adapt.</strong> Cobble together a build from a choice of randomised perks and cards each battle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reinforcements.</strong> Employ mercenaries and heavy support units to join you on heavily infested planets.</p></li></ul>",
